  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Roggerio Rogare</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Lotho_and_Roggerio_Rogare_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Lotho and Roggerio Rogare (The Rise of the Dragon).jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/71/Lotho_and_Roggerio_Rogare_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/350px-Lotho_and_Roggerio_Rogare_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/7/71/Lotho_and_Roggerio_Rogare_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Lotho and Roggerio Rogare at their trial by Ertaç Altinöz for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nLord Roggerio</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li><li>Captain of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Mermaid%27s_Daughter_(ship)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mermaid&#39;s Daughter (ship)\">Mermaid's Daughter</a></i></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">House Rogare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro Rogare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Roggerio Rogare</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">House Rogare</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> noble banking family. He was the son of <a href=\"/index.php/Lysandro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysandro Rogare\">Lysandro Rogare</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Magister_for_Life\" title=\"First Magister for Life\">First Magister</a> of Lys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roggerio_Rogare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Roggerio was the son of Lysandro Rogare. He had five trueborn brothers, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysaro_Rogare\" title=\"Lysaro Rogare\">Lysaro</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Moredo_Rogare\" title=\"Moredo Rogare\">Moredo</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lotho_Rogare\" title=\"Lotho Rogare\">Lotho</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Drako_Rogare\" title=\"Drako Rogare\">Drako</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Fredo_Rogare\" title=\"Fredo Rogare\">Fredo</a>, and three trueborn sisters, <a href=\"/index.php/Larra_Rogare\" title=\"Larra Rogare\">Larra</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysara_Rogare\" title=\"Lysara Rogare\">Lysara</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Marra_Rogare\" title=\"Marra Rogare\">Marra</a>, as well as sixteen <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> siblings.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When his sister Larra came to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> as the wife of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys II Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, Roggerio, Moredo, and Lotho came with her. Roggerio and Lotho were fluent in the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_tongue\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Common tongue\">common tongue</a>, although Moredo was not.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Roggerio opened a high-class <a href=\"/index.php/Pleasure_house\" title=\"Pleasure house\">pleasure house</a> which he called the <a href=\"/index.php/Mermaid_(pillow_house)\" title=\"Mermaid (pillow house)\">Mermaid</a> near the <a href=\"/index.php/River_Gate\" title=\"River Gate\">River Gate</a> in the capital. The Mermaid was no common brothel, but an opulent establishment, full of exotic animals such as <a href=\"/index.php/Parrot\" title=\"Parrot\">parrots</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Monkey\" title=\"Monkey\">monkeys</a>. Its <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitutes\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prostitutes\">prostitutes</a> were exotic too, from every corner of the world and cost ten times more than common whores. Despite this Roggerio never lacked for customers, mainly high <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> and rich merchants. Roggerio banned <a href=\"/index.php/Tessario_the_Tiger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tessario the Tiger\">Tessario the Tiger</a> from the Mermaid when the sellsword struck one of his girls.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a> Roggerio was arrested at the Mermaid by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a> when <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">House Rogare</a> was accused of treason. Although the treason against King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> was later proven unfounded, the new <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Manderly\" title=\"Torrhen Manderly\">Torrhen Manderly</a> still sentenced Roggerio to seven lashes, when Roggerio asked <i>\"for what?\"</i>, Lord Manderly replied <i>\"for being a thrice damned Lyseni\"</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After his punishment and release, he sold his brothel and everything in it to purchase a great <a href=\"/index.php/Ships#Types_of_ships_-_Specifications\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ships\">cog</a> which he named the <a href=\"/index.php/Mermaid%27s_Daughter\" title=\"Mermaid&#39;s Daughter\">Mermaid's Daughter</a>, which effectively was the pillowhouse reborn with sails. Roggerio departed King's Landing and sailed the sea, trading in <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wines</a> and carnal pleasures at every port he visited.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roggerio_Rogare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div s